    "biography": "<p>A giant Awakened lobster (Homarus immanis) thriving in the PCB-enriched coastal waters of the North Sea. Grips prey in its claws and crushes it.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Enhanced Senses (Sonar), Hardened Armor, Immunity to Poisons</p><p><em>Attacks: 5S, Reach +1 (gripping claw). Habitat: Shallow coastal regions, seabeds, estuaries. Range: Coastlines of the North Sea, Scandinavia. Gripping claw: a victim makes a Quickness (4) Test to break free; the grip's Damage Code rises +1 each Combat Turn. Book stats: Body 5/3 (Hardened Armor 3), Intelligence 1/4. PAE p.9.</em></p>",
